How to install:

1.Download file

2.Unpack file to: The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim/data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets

3. Run Skyrim

4.Open racemenu

5.Set race to Nord

6.Set slider for the Preset Slot on slot 15

8.Press F9

9.Have Fun!
